<text:p text:style-name="para">
    Thank you for asking Evolution Lawyers to act for you. We understand that you would like us to assist you with purchasing the Property.
</text:p>

<text:p text:style-name="para">We would be happy to act for you in this matter. Any service we provide to you will be subject to our standard terms, which we have provided to you previously, as varied or added to by this letter of engagement (together, the <text:span text:style-name="bold">Terms</text:span>).
</text:p>

