<text:p text:style-name="el_heading">Your Matter</text:p>
<text:p text:style-name="para">
    The director of Evolution Lawyers with overall responsibility for your matter will be {{ supervisingDirector.name }}. However, the person who will be completing most of the day-to-day attendances required in your matter will be Kieran Boyle, our senior solicitor and conveyancing specialist.
</text:p>

<text:p text:style-name="para">
    If you have any enquiries about your matter, please contact Kieran in the first instance. His contact details are noted at the end of this letter.
</text:p>

<text:p text:style-name="para">
    Alternatively, if you have a simple and non-urgent administrative enquiry, please feel free to contact our administration team by email to mail@evolutionlawyers.nz. Our administration team can deal with most of the non-legal aspects of your matter and may, depending on your enquiry and the firm’s capacity at the time, be able to assist you more promptly than our legal team.
</text:p>

<text:p text:style-name="para">
    In the event you are unable to contact, or are not receiving a timely response from, Kieran or our administration team, or if you have a serious concern or complaint in connection with your matter, please contact the director.
</text:p>

